{"tid":1359323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遍地開花】普通打工仔一人一句致全港市民","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:24:23.000Z","uid":156530,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d363f23283934be2ddd8b36887135b61a229886","tid":1359323,"uid":156530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:13:30.000Z","msg":"我是一位安全主任。<br />\n<br />\n我對特區政府一直漠視民意訴求及高高在上的態度感到反感，由100萬人上街，到200萬+1人上街，以及其後數次的持續遊行仍然視而不見，只作錄音機式回應。而近期警隊的失職更令市民受傷受驚，把香港的治安拖到谷底。我在此呼籲及促請政府正面回應香港市民五大訴求，方能解決你們一直所謂的香港深層次矛盾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnC1iv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnC1iv3.jpg&h=2099f0e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28fd061a2b9e76a65204677b654a0bc408e3f45b","tid":1359323,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19f2136e2ef108f99ba3929348e76a55b6abbea","tid":1359323,"uid":74572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"借位 順手幫推 麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【越洋幫拖】喺美國嘅香港人想收集警暴證據交畀美國警察同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"160fe7f37a631d695c833763e65a0e3dd1e1ee83","tid":1359323,"uid":216253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28fd061a2b9e76a65204677b654a0bc408e3f45b","tid":1359323,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"不入村 不開波 會還拖 先啱呀ching"},{"pid":"a0549ba4ac1d22b7deaaf1d35d7941fb07c8968e","tid":1359323,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:15:54.000Z","msg":"727 和理優 不入村 不開波 會還拖<br />\n<br />\n